title: 14 — Timed Events (Daemon & Fuse)
story: regression
author: Sharpee Regression Suite
description: Verify daemon and fuse both fire during gameplay

---

# Establish the room
> look
[OK: contains "Control Room"]

# Wait until the daemon fires (runOnce, should fire within a few turns)
[DO]
> wait
[UNTIL "FACILITY STATUS"]

# Now wait until the pressure fuse triggers (turns: 8 + skipNextTick)
[DO]
> wait
[UNTIL "WARNING"]
